{"tid":1219924,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（向老師開戰？）教育局長楊潤雄要求學校按條例處理罷課教師","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:40:46.000Z","uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cf703aaee25e6bf7b640a99535fc4f1141765501","tid":1219924,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"【楊潤雄要求學校按條例處理罷課教師】<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄向全港學校校監及校長發信，表示教育局堅決反對罷課和罷教活動，要求學校若教師在工作時間未經學校批准而缺席，校方須按相關條例處理罷課教師。<br />\n來源：港台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z617OdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ617OdR.png&h=8d63c3f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQiJ50w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQiJ50w.png&h=59d6248e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"924a38cf8832792ad0051e7852c9f46e7e86def5","tid":1219924,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"16d7da8c6569ad6f7044d88e965582f5ad69fea0","tid":1219924,"uid":177093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:00:01.000Z","msg":"同教協deal會唔會玩到無限期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e003e43ec54ad2154f57469bad8ba51cad898656","tid":1219924,"uid":247892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"係咪想玩大佢"},{"pid":"333c82223ac41c87b5432447c2f374696d5b3eb3","tid":1219924,"uid":78039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:01:50.000Z","msg":"仲落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632098cd358998dfe14e01217b949d83b3f4608d","tid":1219924,"uid":93900,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:04:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>叫人用和平、合法方式表達意見<br />\n想問下罷課犯左邊條法呀楊潤雄我屌你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e7949ee3005fa45a92b936be0cf