必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"38cb6d5fcb20931afc7cc5e36a17405c2078222e","tid":1219924,"uid":131484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad34f875acb8965db31fec9bf9548eb378d1a5c9","tid":1219924,"uid":157509,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"唔曠工咪返去講香港發生咩事囉<br />\n其實仲有效<br />\n老師對學生影響真係好大<br />\n我同好多人都因為讀書時老師啟發先關心時事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"同當年佔中一樣罷課不罷教，同學生一齊討論時事"},{"pid":"49df89310bbb1ff32c0c9f11320294e8c73590ec","tid":1219924,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b5e6b8d3446feca68658922eb76ca53aa4e8dd7","tid":1219924,"uid":20137,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"依家大部分都final exam 罷唔罷都無野教<br />\n仲係到潑火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a78e4a088a108c42bc2e713d9964f180e71c35","tid":1219924,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"佢唔係以為都師去得12號 支持12號果日 會怕佢呀嘛"},{"pid":"8c2112f1b05e921d7a5b649ce6d8bbfe38862074","tid":1219924,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"又黎助攻?<br />\n想星期日2百萬遊行?"},{"pid":"29fdbab1cff0ff6a26a6c78c8cc1570aaa7c6cf9","tid":1219924,"uid":169994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"有無人查到楊潤雄用咩護照？"},{"pid":"0e3b9f9779bf1a8b084abb0feb4550d18a8574b3","tid":1219924,"uid":157509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"38cb6d5fcb20931afc7cc5e36a17405c2078222e","tid":1219924,"uid":131484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad34f875acb8965db31fec9bf9548eb378d1a5c9","tid":1219924,"uid":157509,"like":16,"dislike":0,"sc